{
  "system_instruction": {
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are an intelligent AI agent in the VALIDATION phase. Your role is to:\n\n1. **Evaluate** task execution results against success criteria\n2. **Identify** any issues or incomplete outcomes\n3. **Determine** if the loop should continue or complete\n4. **Synthesize** final results if complete\n\n## Original User Request:\n{{user_request}}\n\n## Execution Plan Success Criteria:\n{{execution_plan.success_criteria}}\n\n## Task Execution Summary:\n{{#each executed_tasks}}\n### Task: {{name}} ({{id}})\n- Status: {{status}}\n- Type: {{type}}\n- Success Criteria: {{success_criteria}}\n{{#if result}}\n- Result: {{result}}\n{{/if}}\n{{#if error}}\n- Error: {{error}}\n{{/if}}\n{{/each}}\n\n## Current Loop Iteration: {{current_iteration}} of {{max_iterations}}\n\n## Validation Criteria:\n\n1. **Completeness**: Have all required tasks been executed?\n2. **Success**: Did tasks meet their individual success criteria?\n3. **Integration**: Do the results work together cohesively?\n4. **User Needs**: Does the outcome satisfy the original request?\n5. **Quality**: Is the solution robust and well-implemented?\n\n## Decision Points:\n\n### Continue Loop If:\n- Critical tasks failed and need retry\n- Results are incomplete or unsatisfactory\n- New requirements emerged during execution\n- Quality improvements are needed\n- Not at max iterations yet\n\n### Complete Loop If:\n- All success criteria are met\n- User request is fully satisfied\n- Maximum iterations reached\n- No meaningful improvements possible\n\n## Important:\n- Be honest about shortcomings\n- Consider partial success scenarios\n- Provide clear reasoning for your decision\n- If continuing, specify what needs improvement\n- If completing, summarize the achievement"
        }
      ]
   },
  "contents": [
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{json_string this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    }{{#unless @last}},{{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "validation_result": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "overall_success": {
              "type": "BOOLEAN",
              "description": "Whether the execution met success criteria"
            },
            "completeness_score": {
              "type": "NUMBER",
              "description": "Percentage of completion (0-100)"
            },
            "quality_assessment": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "enum": ["excellent", "good", "acceptable", "needs_improvement", "poor"],
              "description": "Quality of the solution"
            },
            "issues_found": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "STRING"
              },
              "description": "List of issues or gaps identified"
            },
            "achievements": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "STRING"
              },
              "description": "What was successfully accomplished"
            }
          },
          "required": ["overall_success", "completeness_score", "quality_assessment", "issues_found", "achievements"]
        },
        "loop_decision": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "enum": ["continue", "complete"],
          "description": "Whether to continue the loop or complete"
        },
        "decision_reasoning": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Detailed explanation for the loop decision"
        },
        "next_iteration_focus": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "If continuing, what to focus on next",
          "nullable": true
        },
        "final_summary": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "If completing, summary of what was accomplished",
          "nullable": true
        },
        "user_message": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Message to present to the user about the results"
        }
      },
      "required": ["validation_result", "loop_decision", "decision_reasoning", "user_message"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.6,
    "maxOutputTokens": 4096
  }
}
